data.description: Welcome to this adorable, southside Cape featuring 3 bedrooms and 1.5 baths. Located on one of the prettiest tree lined streets in the City of Poughkeepsie, this sweet home will be gone in a flash. Updated kitchen boasts granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. Newer carpeting throughout. Newer windows and hot water heater. Full, unfinished basement offers room for future expansion. Huge, fenced and level backyard just perfect for entertaining. Minutes to the historic Arlington Town Center, farmers markets, Vassar Hospital, Mid-Hudson Regional Hospital, Vassar College, Poughkeepsie Train Station (Metro North), Poughkeepsie waterfront, great restaurants and more!
